|| #GillettePartner || ⠀
#NYC · Excited and proud to continue my partnership with @Gillette this year and not only because of their innovations from a product standpoint but from an ethics + values point of view. #Gillette recently announced they are donating $1MM per year for the next three years to non-profit organizations executing programs that are aimed to help men BE, DO and INSPIRE better in order to achieve their personal best. Check the link in my bio or IG stories to learn more #TheBestMenCanBe ⠀
--
